ompose-By-Example/master/screenshots/color_animation.gif&#34; width=&#34;214&#34; height=&#34;400&#34;&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;  &lt;/tr&gt; &#xA;  &lt;tr&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/theme/DarkModeActivity.kt&#34;&gt;How do styles &amp;amp; themes work in Jetpack Compose?&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/theme/DarkModeActivity.kt&#34;&gt;How do I add dark mode capability to my app?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/master/screenshots/dark_mode.gif&#34; width=&#34;214&#34; height=&#34;400&#34;&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;  &lt;/tr&gt; &#xA; &lt;/tbody&gt; &#xA;&lt;/table&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;State Management&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;table&gt; &#xA; &lt;thead&gt; &#xA;  &lt;tr&gt; &#xA;   &lt;th&gt;Example&lt;/th&gt; &#xA;   &lt;th&gt;Preview&lt;/th&gt; &#xA;  &lt;/tr&gt; &#xA; &lt;/thead&gt; &#xA; &lt;tbody&gt; &#xA;  &lt;tr&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/state/StateActivity.kt&#34;&gt;How do I store state information in Jetpack Compose?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/master/screenshots/state_example.gif&#34; width=&#34;214&#34; height=&#34;400&#34;&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;  &lt;/tr&gt; &#xA;  &lt;tr&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/state/ProcessDeathActivity.kt&#34;&gt;How do I retain state across process death &amp;amp; activity recreation(like orientation changes)?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&