ample/jetpackcompose/state/backpress/BackPressActivity.kt&#34;&gt;How do you handle back press in Jetpack Compose?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/master/screenshots/back_press.gif&#34; width=&#34;214&#34; height=&#34;400&#34;&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;  &lt;/tr&gt; &#xA; &lt;/tbody&gt; &#xA;&lt;/table&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;Material Design&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;table&gt; &#xA; &lt;thead&gt; &#xA;  &lt;tr&gt; &#xA;   &lt;th&gt;Example&lt;/th&gt; &#xA;   &lt;th&gt;Preview&lt;/th&gt; &#xA;  &lt;/tr&gt; &#xA; &lt;/thead&gt; &#xA; &lt;tbody&gt; &#xA;  &lt;tr&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/material/MaterialActivity.kt#L114&#34;&gt;How do I add a Material Design Card?&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/material/MaterialActivity.kt#L272&#34;&gt;How do I display a linear progress bar?&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/material/MaterialActivity.kt#L325&#34;&gt;What about a circular progress bar?&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/material/MaterialActivity.kt#L367&#34;&gt;How do I add a Snackbar?&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/material/MaterialActivity.kt#L393&#34;&gt;How to add a Material Design Slider?&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/material/MaterialActivity.kt#L196&