&#xA;&lt;table&gt; &#xA; &lt;thead&gt; &#xA;  &lt;tr&gt; &#xA;   &lt;th&gt;Example&lt;/th&gt; &#xA;   &lt;th&gt;Preview&lt;/th&gt; &#xA;  &lt;/tr&gt; &#xA; &lt;/thead&gt; &#xA; &lt;tbody&gt; &#xA;  &lt;tr&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/main/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/interop/ComposeInClassicAndroidActivity.kt&#34;&gt;How can I use Jetpack Compose components inside existing screens?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/master/screenshots/interop.png&#34; width=&#34;214&#34; height=&#34;400&#34;&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;  &lt;/tr&gt; &#xA; &lt;/tbody&gt; &#xA;&lt;/table&gt; &#xA;&lt;h3&gt;Testing&lt;/h3&gt; &#xA;&lt;table&gt; &#xA; &lt;thead&gt; &#xA;  &lt;tr&gt; &#xA;   &lt;th&gt;Example&lt;/th&gt; &#xA;   &lt;th&gt;Preview&lt;/th&gt; &#xA;  &lt;/tr&gt; &#xA; &lt;/thead&gt; &#xA; &lt;tbody&gt; &#xA;  &lt;tr&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/vinaygaba/Learn-Jetpack-Compose-By-Example/raw/master/app/src/androidTest/java/com/example/jetpackcompose/text/SimpleTextComposableTest.kt&#34;&gt;How do I write a simple UI Test in Jetpack Compose? &lt;br&gt; How do I test &#34;Composables&#34;?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;   &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt; &#xA;  &lt;/tr&gt; &#xA; &lt;/tbody&gt; &#xA;&lt;/table&gt; &#xA;&lt;h2&gt;Credits&lt;/h2&gt; &#xA;&lt;p&gt;Author: Vinay Gaba (&lt;a href=&#34;mailto:vinaygaba@gmail.com&#34;&gt;vinaygaba@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt; &#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://twitter.com/vinaygaba&#34;&gt; &lt;img alt=&#34;Follow me on Twitter&#34; src=&#34;https://github.com/gabrielemariotti/cardslib/raw/master/demo/images/twitter64.png&#34;&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.linkedin.com/in/vinaygaba&#34;&gt; &lt;img alt=&#34;Follow me on LinkedIn&#34; src=&#34;https://github.com/gabrielemariotti/cardslib/raw/master/demo/images/linkedin.png&#34;&gt